          <http://dbpedia.org/property/relatives>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludwig_Von_Drake> ;
          <http://dbpedia.org/property/relatives>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huey,_Dewey,_and_Louie> ;
